    {
      "type": "table",
      "title": "Trend · 交易所持仓（账户 reconcile，`strategy` 固定为 `all`）",
      "description": "**数据源**：`METRICS.update_account_data()` → Binance Futures `GET /fapi/v2/account` 的 **`positions`**，经 `update_position_metrics(..., strategy=\"all\")` 写入 Gauges。**不是** archetype/`PositionTracker` 内部台账。\n\n**为何和「入场价 / entry 打点」可对不上**：上图 **`mlbot_strategy_event_price`** 的 `strategy` = **archetype（如 tpc）**；本表 **`strategy`** 恒为 **`all`**（交易所在单账户上不区分内置策略）。`entry` 在 **挂单成功回路**打点，**不能保证**几秒后的 scrape 上仍有净仓（未成交、已平、被拒、或减少为 0）。\n\n**为何曾出现 qty=0 仍占一行**：Grafana **instant** 会合并曾为非零的标签组合；已对 PromQL **`> 0`** 过滤，空仓不再占行。**上方策略变量不参与本表**（避免误筛掉 `strategy=all` 序列）。`symbol` 变量仍生效。",
      "id": 307,
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 51
      },
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prometheus-monitoring"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "max by (strategy, symbol, side) (mlbot_position_qty{job=~\"$job\",scope=\"trend\",strategy=\"all\",symbol=~\"${symbol:regex}\"}) > 0",
          "format": "table",
          "instant": true
        },
        {
          "refId": "B",
          "expr": "max by (strategy, symbol, side) (mlbot_position_notional_usdt{job=~\"$job\",scope=\"trend\",strategy=\"all\",symbol=~\"${symbol:regex}\"}) > 0",
          "format": "table",
          "instant": true
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {},
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "showHeader": true
      }
    },
